===Etymology===
Same word as {{och-l|驛|posthorse; relay station}}, {{och-l|譯|to translate}}, {{och-l|懌|relaxed; pleased}}, {{och-l|斁|id=3|to be tired of}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). Also related to {{och-l|釋|to set free; to explain}}, {{och-l|赦|to let go; to pardon}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). This word family may be related to {{cog|my|လျက်|t=while; although}} ({{zh-ref|Luce, 1981}}).

